snippet.title: Veiled Skies Trailer
snippet.description:
Final trailer for Veiled Skies, releasing on 22 August, 2024 on Steam.

Step into a world above the clouds, into a cloudpunk fantasy with foxgirls! Heavily inspired by Granblue Fantasy and Arknights (character design).
